text: Sebastian [ si-bas-chuhn ] is a name. It comes from the Greek name Sebastianos (Σεβαστιανός) or changed into English "from Sebastia". It is given to people a lot because of a saint called Sebastian. This name was ranked #19 on the US Popular Names in 2021. == PEOPLE == * Sebastian Vettel, German racing driver * Sebastian Coe, British athlete and politician (born 1956) * Sebastian Giovinco, Italian footballer == References == Category:Given names
title: Sebastian
